# 新增 / 修改 OpenAkita 内置工具时必读

每个内置工具必须有显式 `ApprovalClass` 声明,
否则 `pytest tests/unit/test_classifier_completeness.py` 红灯,
启动时也会输出 `[Policy] Tool 'xxx' has no explicit ApprovalClass` WARN.

完整 SOP + 4 个方案见 [docs/policy_v2_research.md §4.21](mdc:docs/policy_v2_research.md)

## 推荐做法 (方案 C — handler 自治)

新工具属于现有 handler 时, 在 handler 类的 `TOOL_CLASSES` 字典加一行:

```python
class FilesystemHandler:
    TOOLS = ["read_file", "write_file", "my_new_tool"]
    TOOL_CLASSES = {
        "read_file": ApprovalClass.READONLY_GLOBAL,
        "write_file": ApprovalClass.MUTATING_SCOPED,
        "my_new_tool": ApprovalClass.MUTATING_SCOPED,  # ← 新增
    }
```

## 备选 (方案 B — agent.py 集中声明)

```python
self.handler_registry.register(
    "filesystem", create_filesystem_handler(self),
    tool_classes={"my_new_tool": ApprovalClass.MUTATING_SCOPED},
)
```

## 11 类 ApprovalClass 速查

`READONLY_GLOBAL` `READONLY_SCOPED` `READONLY_SEARCH` `MUTATING_SCOPED`
`MUTATING_GLOBAL` `DESTRUCTIVE` `EXEC_LOW_RISK` `EXEC_CAPABLE`
`CONTROL_PLANE` `INTERACTIVE` `UNKNOWN`

不确定挑哪类 → 优先选更严的 (safety-by-default), classifier 的 `most_strict`
会保留更高严格度.

## 行为依赖参数 (例: 写入路径决定风险)

→ 修改 `policy_v2/classifier.py:_refine_with_params`,
  并在 `tests/unit/test_classifier.py` 加 case 覆盖新分支.

## Skill / MCP / Plugin 工具不在此列

第三方扩展通过 SKILL.md frontmatter / MCP `tool.annotations` /
plugin manifest 各自声明 — 不需要改本仓代码.
